videos.description: Western Michigan's Jon Wassink finds Brett Borske in the end zone for a 17-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Western Michigan's Borske scores 17-yard TD

videos.description: Georgia State quarterback Dan Ellington gets a block and reaches for the pylon on a 10-yard score vs. Western Michigan.
videos.headline: Georgia State QB dives for the pylon on TD run

videos.description: Jon Wassink fits a 24-yard touchdown pass in a narrow window to Keishawn Watson.
videos.headline: Western Michigan's Wassink throws 2nd TD pass

videos.description: Jamauri Bogan makes a cut and leaves Georgia State defenders in the dust for a 71-yard touchdown scamper.
videos.headline: Bogan sprints 71 yards for Western Michigan TD
